Blocks.Text: We define quantum replicator dynamics by taking continuous time limit of MMWU.
The quantum replicator dynamics are Poincaré recurrent in any two-
player zero-sum game which has a fully-mixed Nash equilibrium.
Like classical setting, need to prove bounded orbits and volume preservation, but classical
strategy fails due to non-commutativity of terms!
